%%Page: 3 3
TitleFont
(Operational Flow And Exceptions) 50 792 T

HeadFont
(Typical Work Flow) 50 748 T
BodyFont
(1. A member joins in ClubSpark.) 70 722 T
(2. ClubSpark sends a notification email and updates its member/contact records.) 70 704 T
(3. n8n captures the email and refreshes the latest ClubSpark exports.) 70 686 T
(4. The local database combines those sources into a clean signup record.) 70 668 T
(5. A batch is created for new items that need to be fulfilled.) 70 650 T
(6. The batch produces labels, envelope PDFs, and exception lists.) 70 632 T
(7. Where an address is missing, the member can be contacted by email instead of post.) 70 614 T
(8. Once the physical admin work is done, the batch is marked complete.) 70 596 T
(9. Reporting is synced to Metabase so the committee can monitor progress.) 70 578 T

HeadFont
(Exception Handling) 50 528 T
BodyFont
(- Missing signup capture: if ClubSpark shows a valid membership but no signup email was captured,) 70 502 T
(  the workflow can create the missing record.) 70 484 T
(- No-address handling: if there is no usable postal address, the system can send an email instead) 70 458 T
(  of producing post.) 70 440 T
(- Manual batch items: extra shoe tags, parent tags, or keys can be added without pretending there) 70 414 T
(  was a new signup.) 70 396 T
(- History snapshots: periodic snapshots preserve membership counts for trend reporting over time.) 70 370 T

HeadFont
(Summary) 50 320 T
BodyFont
(At a committee level, the system can be thought of as a membership operations pipeline:) 50 294 T
(- ClubSpark provides the raw membership events and data) 70 268 T
(- n8n turns that into usable admin work) 70 250 T
(- the local database tracks what has happened and what still needs doing) 70 232 T
(- print files, emails, and dashboards are the outputs the committee sees) 70 214 T
(The main benefit is that signups, address handling, batch preparation, and reporting are kept in one) 50 176 T
(joined-up process instead of being managed manually across separate spreadsheets and inboxes.) 50 158 T
showpage

